# Fix_Google_Play — Method 3: route via proxy
#
# googleapis.cn (incl. services.googleapis.cn) must go through proxy
# so Google returns a global CDN URL, not CN CDN.
# xn--ngstr-lra8j.com is .com → caught by geolocation-!cn → proxy automatically.
# Both end up on the same proxy path → consistent.
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,googleapis.cn
DOMAIN,clientservices.googleapis.com
DOMAIN,update.googleapis.com
DOMAIN,fonts.googleapis.com
